 《Killing Joke》吉他手乔迪·沃克去世，享年 64 岁https://www.nme.com/news/music/killing-joke-guitarist-geordie-walker-has-died-ged-64-3549275?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=killing-joke-guitarist-geordie-walker-已去世，年龄 64 岁NMESun, 26 Nov 2023 20:28:32 +0000 Music NewsNews..Rock https://www.nme.com/?p=3549275 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Geordie-Walker-credit-Getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="乔迪·沃克" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Geordie-Walker-credit-Getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Geordie-Walker-credit-Getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Geordie-Walker-credit-Getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Geordie-Walker-credit-Getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Geordie-Walker-credit-Getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Geordie-Walker-credit-Getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>马丁·阿特金斯证实了这一消息</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/killing-joke-guitarist-geordie-walker-has-died-aged-64-3549275">Killing Joke 后吉他手乔迪·沃克 (Geordie Walker) 去世，享年 64 岁，</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Geordie-Walker-credit-Getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="乔迪·沃克" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Geordie-Walker-credit-Getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Geordie-Walker-credit-Getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Geordie-Walker-credit-Getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Geordie-Walker-credit-Getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Geordie-Walker-credit-Getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Geordie-Walker-credit-Getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/killng-joke">《Killing Joke》</a>吉他手凯文·“乔迪”·沃克去世，享年 64 岁。</p><p>该消息于今晚（11 月 26 日）发布在 Killing Joke 前鼓手马丁·阿特金斯 (Martin Atkins) 的 Facebook 页面上。他分享了《伤害手册》的“笑道”的视频——他们也是这个超级组合的一部分——标题是“内脏”。他还在评论区写道：“乔迪已经去世了。”</p><p>他后来还在 Twitter/X 上发帖写道：“#GodBless Geordie Walker”。</p><p>乐队今晚发表声明称他们“悲痛欲绝”，并证实沃克于 11 月 26 日死于中风。</p><p>乐队在 Instagram 上的声明中写道：“我们极其悲伤地确认，2023 年 11 月 26 日上午 6 点 30 分，Killing Joke 的传奇吉他手凯文·乔迪·沃克 (Kevin ‘Geordie’ Walker) 因中风去世，他的家人陪伴在他身边。我们很伤心。兄弟安息吧。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C0IDaLhCgP4/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fil